---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Social & PPC Campaigns - Florida Marketing Agency'
	description='Paid campaigns only work when the targeting, creative, and landing experience support the same goal. We manage social and PPC campaigns that put the right message in front of the right people at the right time.'
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Digital Marketing Services' title='Social & PPC' description="Paid campaigns only work when the targeting, creative, and landing experience support the same goal. We manage social and PPC campaigns that put the right message in front of the right people at the right time." lottieFile='social-media-content.json' />
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>Paid media gets expensive fast when clicks are arriving but the campaigns are not producing meaningful movement. In most cases, the problem is not the platform alone. It is the mismatch between targeting, creative, offer, and landing experience.</p>
			<p>That is why some businesses keep spending more while learning very little.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<p>We treat paid media like a system. Audience strategy, campaign structure, creative direction, testing, and reporting all need to support the same outcome so the spend has a real chance to perform.</p>
			<h2>Platforms we work with</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Facebook</li>
				<li>Twitter</li>
				<li>Instagram</li>
				<li>LinkedIn</li>
				<li>Google Ads</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If you want paid media to become a more predictable growth channel instead of an ongoing experiment, we can review the current setup, identify where spend is leaking, and recommend the first places to tighten the strategy.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Review Your Paid Strategy</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={86} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
